---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="/now — Dino Favara Jr."
  description="What Dino Favara Jr. is actually working on, reading, and thinking about right now. Updated March 2026."
>
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-14 pb-10">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-[520px] h-[520px] rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-[100px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-40 -right-20 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-periwinkle/15 blur-[80px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 w-[260px] h-[260px] rounded-full bg-mint/8 blur-[72px]"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="h-px w-10 bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary/80">
            Updated March 2026
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem)] leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-dark mb-5">
          /now
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[1.1rem] font-light text-dark/60 leading-relaxed">
          What I'm actually working on, reading, and thinking about.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Content ── -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20 space-y-16">

      <!-- What I'm Building -->
      <section class="border-t border-dark/8 pt-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px w-10 bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary/70">Active</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-dark mb-7">What I'm building</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {[
            { text: 'dinofavarajr.com (this site)', note: 'Building a home base for everything I make.' },
            { text: 'Short Form Secrets newsletter', note: 'Growing to 1,000 subscribers. Currently at 470+ and climbing.' },
            { text: 'YouTube strategy for a finance client', note: 'Developing a content system that compounds over time.' },
            { text: 'Disney park content for spring 2026', note: 'A new batch of park guides and ride breakdowns.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="mt-[0.45rem] flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
              <div>
                <span class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark">{item.text}</span>
                <span class="text-[1rem] font-light text-dark/55"> — {item.note}</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- What I'm Consuming -->
      <section class="border-t border-dark/8 pt-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px w-10 bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary/70">Consuming</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-dark mb-7">What I'm consuming</h2>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xl select-none mt-0.5">📖</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Reading</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark">Dune — Frank Herbert</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">Been at it for about a year. It's dense, rewarding, and I just discovered there's an appendix. AN APPENDIX!? Nobody told me.</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark mt-3">A Guide to the Good Life — William B. Irvine</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">An intro to Stoicism that's actually readable. Slowly working its way into how I think about work and what I choose to care about.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xl select-none mt-0.5">📺</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Watching</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark">One Piece Live Action — Season 2</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">It's better than people say. Yes, it's corny. But One Piece IS corny — so it's perfect. Every casting choice is beautifully done. It's believable, doesn't take itself too seriously, and feels just like the anime. Which is exactly what it should be.</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/40 mt-2">Also: Survivor Season 50. Christian Hubicki is my spirit animal.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xl select-none mt-0.5">🎧</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Listening</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark">Wes Huff podcast appearances</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">The man is a walking bible encyclopedia and I'm here for it. Jenny and I listened to his episode of Joe Rogan on the way to the beach the other day and it got us hooked.</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark mt-3">Alex Hormozi business clips</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">Background fuel. Good for when you need to think bigger about what you're building.</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark mt-3">Walt Disney: The Triumph of the American Imagination — Neal Gabler</p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">Audiobook. The man was obsessive, complicated, and relentless. Hard not to be inspired and slightly unsettled at the same time.</p>
              <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium text-dark mt-3">
                <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5NLmKePHYfRDdLP5j2VryS?si=b8da923424154e06" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">My 90s Playlist ↗</a>
              </p>
              <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-light text-dark/55 mt-0.5">The cure for everything.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What Matters Most -->
      <section class="border-t border-dark/8 pt-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px w-10 bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary/70">Home base</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-dark mb-7">What matters most right now</h2>
        <p class="text-[1.05rem] font-light text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
          Jenny and I are deep in the good chaos of raising two boys — Dino III and River. We're figuring it out one day at a time, leaning on faith, and trying to be present for the small stuff. That's the whole game.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer note -->
      <p class="text-sm font-light text-dark/35 italic border-t border-dark/6 pt-8">
        Last updated March 2026. Inspired by{' '}
        <a
          href="https://nownownow.com/about"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-primary/60 transition-colors"
        >
          Derek Sivers' /now movement
        </a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
